"{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8ade9708dfacf1070e6f5c99cb&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;E9: Fiscal Dominance, the War in Ukraine's Actual Cost, and Fact Checking Rich Men North of Richmond&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/3CIWHPMlGBUXs210im2gxO&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/3CIWHPMlGBUXs210im2gxO" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这里是<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/e9-fiscal-dominance-actual-spend-on-the-war-in/id1696419056?i=1000626778327">Apple 播客</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErP3GCMRMQ4">YouTube</a>的链接。</p><p> Brad DeLong 和我还有另一集 Hexapodia，其中我们谈论经济发展，以及为什么 20 世纪 50 年代的简单增长模型实际上比基于政治经济学的更复杂的理论更好地预测了中国的增长： </p><div class="embedded-post-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:136740133,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://braddelong.substack.com/p/podcast-hexapodia-lii-growth-development&quot;,&quot;publication_id&quot;:47874,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Brad DeLong's Grasping Reality&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffde2453e-9c18-4560-82ca-8b77ae62ef5b_1280x1280.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;PODCAST: Hexapodia LII: Growth, Development, China, the Solow Model, &amp; the Future of South &amp; Southeast Asia&quot;,&quot;truncated_body_text&quot;:&quot;Listen now (50 mins) | &quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2023-09-05T02:23:32.291Z&quot;,&quot;like_count&quot;:14,&quot;comment_count&quot;:14,&quot;bylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:16879,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Brad DeLong&quot;,&quot;handle&quot;:&quot;delongonsubstack&quot;,&quot;previous_name&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;http